author: Crystal L.
title: Crystal L.
text: Ended up ordering the replacement antenna online by myself because it was after hours when the guy finally called me back. Once I attached new antenna, it ended up being defective as I later came to find out the solder had cracked where the antenna is attached to the cable & no one will help me replace it.
